{"id":"guide/i18n-common-add-package","title":"新增 localize 套件","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"add-the-localize-package\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4byiubykxo4pfqxbc605ynmub\">新增 localize 套件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d3j927n3cvrvfeg7pyelrgk2y\">要利用 Angular 的本地化功能，請用 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 將 <code>@angular/localize</code> 套件新增到你的專案中。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"aez6046rapr7w085862v674kh\">要新增 <code>@angular/localize</code> 套件，請使用如下指令來更新專案中的 <code>package.json</code> 和 <code>polyfills.ts</code> 檔案。</p>\n<code-example path=\"i18n/doc-files/commands.sh\" region=\"add-localize\">\nng add @angular/localize\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ehftwq340aplvyioic7lwo2ow\">它在 TypeScript 設定檔案中新增 <code>types: [\"@angular/localize\"]</code>，並在 <code>main.ts</code> 檔案頂部新增對 <code>@angular/localize</code> 型別定義的引用。</p>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7f5glmrmsbdmmbw1j25b9usa2\">有關 <code>package.json</code> 和 <code>polyfill</code> 套件的更多訊息，請參閱<a href=\"guide/npm-packages\" title=\"Workspace npm dependencies | Angular\">工作區的 npm 依賴項</a>。</p>\n</div>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6uzdpvfm1je458sa51izimghg\">如果尚未安裝 <code>@angular/localize</code>，而你試圖建立此項目的本地化版本，<a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 就會報錯。</p>\n<h2 id=\"options\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cyk2rtnidu0xcswyg7218m57s\">選項<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">OPTION</th>\n<th align=\"left\">DESCRIPTION</th>\n<th align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8glwd2ohrnmnjec1hpn434ynv\">值型別</th>\n<th align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"64bf36k4ahul8lj702zguv4qw\">預設值</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>--project</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"agjqi42ykk7wq2xj1xt1qtgfa\">專案名稱。</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>string</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>--use-at-runtime</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4c2u8r7sg8fy7jyvj5c7r1fv0\">如果設定，則可以在執行時使用 \n<code><a href=\"api/localize/init/$localize\" class=\"code-anchor\">$localize</a></code>。此外，\n<code>@angular/localize</code> 將包含在 \n<code>package.json</code> 的 \n<code>dependencies</code> 部分中，而不是 \n<code>devDependencies</code>，這是預設值。</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>boolean</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code>false</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"drumim626lrzzfca0v9ghon75\">要了解更多可用選項，請參閱 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 中的 <a href=\"cli/add\" title=\"ng add | CLI | Angular\">ng add</a>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"whats-next\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"407r2fj2mi5kvg7imj9zdcpe\">下一步呢？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#whats-next\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7lab03aiwzepwsz8x6trg367f\"><a href=\"api/localize\" title=\"$localize | @angular/localize - API | Angular\">@angular/localize API</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9lxl8lkbvn4wdjsmave6ltdsz\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID | Angular\">透過 ID 引用語音環境</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：Fri Mar 10 2023</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-common-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/localize\n - api/localize/init/$localize\n - cli\n - cli/add\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#options\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#whats-next\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/npm-packages\n - guide/typescript-configuration\n-->"}